  "comment": "Решение:\nТ.к. \\((x^2-36)^2 \\geq 0\\) и \\((x^2+4x-12)^2 \\geq 0, \\Rightarrow (x^2-36)^2+(x^2+4x-12)^2\\geq 0\\) только когда\n\\(\\begin{cases}x^2-36=0 (1) \\\\x^2+4x-12=0 (2)\\end{cases}\\)\n\\((1) x^2-36=0\\)\n\\((x-6)(x+6)=0\\)\n\\((2) x^2+4x-12=0\\)\n\\(D=16+48=64\\)\n\\(x_1=\\cfrac{-4-8}{2}\\)\n\\(x_1=-6\\)\n\\(x_2=\\cfrac{-4+8}{2}\\)\n\\(x_2=2\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}(x-6)(x+6)=0 \\\\x=-6; x=2\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}x=6; x=-6 \\\\x=-6; x=2\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\Rightarrow x=-6\\\\\\)\nОтвет:\\(-6\\)",
